  "answer": "**Chapter 75 of *Diwan-E-Ghalib* is titled \"Hujoom-e-naala-e-hairat aajiz-e-arz-e-yak-afghaan hai\".**[^1]\n\nThis is one of Mirza Ghalib's ghazals (verse chapters), opening with the line: \"A flood of sighs leaves wonder helpless to complain\".[^2]\n\n[^1]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, [ch. 75](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/75-hujoom-e-naala-e-hairat-aajiz-e-arz-e-yak-afghaan-/translation/).\n\n[^2]: Mirza Ghalib, *Diwan-E-Ghalib*, [ch. 75, p-ae96a3](/works/mirza-ghalib-diwan-e-ghalib-74ed4c/75-hujoom-e-naala-e-hairat-aajiz-e-arz-e-yak-afghaan-/translation/#p-ae96a3).",
